text.section:
The membership of the board shall be as follows:
A member of the county legislative body of Sumner County, Tennessee, and Simpson County, Kentucky, chosen by their respective legislative bodies;
The mayors of the cities of Portland, Tennessee, and Franklin, Kentucky;
A member of the city legislative bodies from the cities of Portland, Tennessee, and Franklin, Kentucky, chosen by the respective legislative bodies;
A member of an industrial foundation board or equivalent, if one (1) exists, from Portland, Tennessee, and Franklin, Kentucky, as appointed by the respective boards; and
A commissioner or designee chosen by the board of commissioners of the Simpson County water district.
